{"tid":2369731,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港真有「貧窮問題」嗎？- 古德明","createTime":"2021-01-17T11:38:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T13:26:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"28c0531c96843a33a548caa00ec8698a429d79f3","tid":2369731,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T11:38:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210117/ZNUCPIMSBJG5DJ4TCXRGRSW724/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210117%2FZNUCPIMSBJG5DJ4TCXRGRSW724%2F&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHGvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=6887df31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210117%2FZNUCPIMSBJG5DJ4TCXRGRSW724%2F&h=260cbd71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210117/ZNUCPIMSBJG5DJ4TCXRGRSW724/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n香港真有「貧窮問題」嗎？- 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/f0zkZQW5Q_nqgAA754rbSlac4gM=/1654x1103/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AOIUORS4OFFMVEK4TUO7ZJKDSE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ff0zkZQW5Q_nqgAA754rbSlac4gM%3D%2F1654x1103%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAOIUORS4OFFMVEK4TUO7ZJKDSE.jpg&h=f3d2badc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上月二十三日，鄭月娥政府發表《二零一九年香港貧窮情況報告》，謂港人貧困者有一百四十九萬一千，佔人口超過兩成，是二零零九年有紀錄以來最多。但這統計恐難取信於人。或曰：「此而不信，孰可信也？」則必曰：「我信黨。」<br />\n<br />\n按中共國務院上月十四日召開「人類減貧經驗國際論壇」，習近平同志擲下賀函，鄭重宣布天大喜訊：「今年，中國現行標準之下，農村人口已經全部脫貧，對全球減貧事業貢獻巨大。」根據「中國現行標準」，每人每年收入超過三千八百二十港元，生活已是小康。而鄭月娥政府現在奉行的標準，則是一口之家，每月收入少於四千五百元，即屬貧困。以每月四千五百元較諸每年三千八百二十元，香港所謂貧困者，分明已是富豪。大陸生活水準雖然比香港低一點，相差總沒有「每年三千多元」與「每月四千多元」那麼大吧。可見香港其實沒有貧窮問題，問題只在於港人過於富有。<br />\n<br />\n所以，新香港歷任政府，都。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"d4800738569b07990911fb152787046ff43447a9","tid":2369731,"uid":388055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T11:41:21.000Z","msg":"妓女可信<br />\n共產黨不可信"},{"pid":"4c466f9a91e9ba2b70ac79214a0a13631d2fe554","tid":2369731,"uid":235665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T13:26:43.000Z","msg":"共產黨：中國無窮人！"}]}